sentence: willie j. daniels| willie j. daniels age 46, of west palm beach, florida.
passed away suddenly on tuesday, june 2, 2015.
willie was a laborer in construction for many years locally.
he leaves to mourn his passing his six brothers; joseph b. hunter, carl hunter, michael hunter, alvert daniels, alfred (yolanda) daniels and paris l. daniels.
and a host of many relatives and friends.
